# Browser Support Configuration for SmartBudget
# This configuration aligns with the official support statement in BETA_TESTING.md
# Supported: Latest versions of Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge
# NOT supported: Internet Explorer

# Production browsers
# Target modern browsers with good ES2017+ and CSS support
> 0.5%
last 2 versions
not dead
not IE 11

# Explicitly include modern browsers
Chrome >= 90
Firefox >= 88
Safari >= 14
Edge >= 90

# Mobile browsers
iOS >= 14
Android >= 90

# Exclude old and unsupported browsers
not IE 11
not op_mini all
